                          1. Comments
What is it?
-----------
This is the second chapter of the CodeGlyph.
It is dedicated to documentation within the code with the use of comments
Points covered:
    - Language comments
    - Special language documentation constructs (javadoc,perldoc,...)
    - Doxygen documentation

Authors
-------
topo@skull-coding-krew.org

Execution
----------
C/C++ (with make)
> make main
> target/C++/main.exe

More documentation
------------------
> doxygen doc/doxyfile (also make doc)
